title: #92Noon Live from the Combine! Cronin / Cosell / Norv / Farwell / Spielman / Clayton
description:
PA, Charch, and Leber are live from the NFL Combine in Indianapolis for Day 2!

The guest lineup includes ESPN's Courtney Cronin, NFL Films' Greg Cosell, Bills Coach Heath Farwell, Vikings GM Rick Spielman, and ESPN's John Clayton.
